Here's an idea a druid on my old server (Rallos) used to justify killing animals:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> If</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> you put to good use what you find (cook the meats, sew the pelts, etc.) then it is acceptable to take from the land around you.<br>
<br>
If you kill wantonly then you are abusing the powers Tunare has given you.<br>
<br>
